### Genfeed API - Agent Orchestrator Endpoints
### Starts agent turns and exposes agent account-level resources.

########################################
# Agent Turns
########################################

### Start Agent Turn In New Thread
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/turns
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Plan my next content sprint.",
  "source": "agent"
}


### Start Agent Turn In Existing Thread
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}/turns
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Continue from the last plan.",
  "source": "agent"
}


### Start Streaming Agent Turn In New Thread
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/turns/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Generate a content plan for this week.",
  "source": "agent"
}


### Start Streaming Agent Turn In Existing Thread
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}/turns/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Turn this into tasks.",
  "source": "agent"
}


########################################
# Agent Resources
########################################

### Get Agent Credits
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/credits
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### List Agent Goals
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/goals
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
